# Lint

When user asks to lint or audit wiki:

- Check contradictions between pages
- Find orphan pages (no inbound links)
- Identify concepts mentioned without own page
- Flag claims outdated based on newer sources
- Check all pages follow page format
- Report findings as numbered list with suggested fixes
